<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #22C55E; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 20px; background: #f8f9fa; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>ðŸŽ‰ Payment Confirmed!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</h2>
      
      <p>Great news! Your payment for <strong><%= @registration.business_name %></strong> has been successfully processed.</p>
      
      <p><strong>Payment Details:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Amount: <%= @payment.formatted_amount %></li>
        <li>Payment Method: <%= @payment.payment_method.humanize %></li>
        <li>Transaction ID: <%= @payment.transaction_id %></li>
        <li>Date: <%= @payment.paid_at.strftime('%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p') %></li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>Your documents are now being reviewed by our compliance team. You'll receive your official incorporation documents within 1-2 business days.</p>
      
      <p>Thank you for choosing Corppy!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>